      "content": "\"an obligation to stay\"... that's exactly it. it feels like i'm just being forced to watch a slow-motion train wreck for no reason. if the end is just inevitable anyway, then isn't there more dignity in just choosing when to leave? i'm so tired of the struggle. it just seems so much more logical to just opt out of this mess.",
